title: Goody Heat Smart Temp Blow Dryer
description: The only dryer smart enough to give you 10 heat settings, the new Goody HEAT Smart Temp Blow Dryer makes it easy to customize your blowout. A patented Heat Control Dial lets you control your dryer’s temperature to find the perfect heat for any hair type, styling occasion, or style.  The dryer is infused with frizz-reducing ceramic and ionic technologies to create beautiful hair at any temperature.  Customize your blowout with the new Smart Temp dryer!
